Barbershop;;62;;83;;PG-13;;A smart comedy about a day in the life of a barbershop on the south side of Chicago. Calvin (Ice Cube), who inherited the struggling business from his deceased father, views the shop as nothing but a burden and a waste of his time. After selling the shop to a local loan shark, Calvin slowly begins to see his father's vision and legacy and struggles with the notion that he just sold it out.;;Comedy;;Tim Story;;2002;;Ice Cube,Anthony Anderson,Cedric the Entertainer,Sean Patrick Thomas,Eve,Troy Garity,Michael Ealy,Leonard Earl Howze,Keith David,Jazsmin Lewis,Lahmard Tate,Tom Wright;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/barbershop